<h2>Done in this round</h2>
<div class="my-2"><strong>Pricing restructured and verified</strong> — <a href="https://github.com/kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site/pull/6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">PR #6</a> is up, with visual proof from the preview deployment:</div>
