</ul>
<div class="my-2"><strong>Domain config complete:</strong> <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">www</code> now 308-redirects to the apex (matching your canonical tags), verified live. And my probes confirmed what you quietly shipped while we talked pricing: <strong>PRs #4/#5 merged, the hardened Wattle &amp; Crumb site is live on <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">replyhive.com.au</code>, the origin gate is rejecting forged requests, and <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">RESEND_API_KEY</code> is set — your lead form works right now.</strong> The funnel is open. 🐝</div>
<h2>The last login</h2>
<div class="my-2">The shared browser is on the <strong>VIPControl login page</strong>. Log in there (same live view window), reply "in", and I'll enter the four Resend DNS records myself — then click Verify in Resend (still logged in from round 1) and run the final end-to-end check. This one's not launch-blocking (leads already deliver via Resend's shared sender), it just moves your emails onto <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">@replyhive.com.au</code> for deliverability and polish.</div>
<div class="my-2">Two small things for your list afterwards: merge PR #6 when you're happy with the screenshot, and drag <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">og.jpg</code> (from earlier in this thread) into the repo root so shared links unfurl with your brand card.</div></div><div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"><a href="https://github.com/kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site/pull/6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group inline-flex h-16 w-44 items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border bg-card p-2 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50"><div data-slot="icon-tile" class="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-md bg-muted text-muted-foreground overflow-hidden"><img alt="" class="size-full object-cover" src="./og_files/6"></div><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-0.5"><span class="line-clamp-2 font-medium text-foreground text-xs leading-tight">Pricing: Founding Client offer, Standard anchor, annual option by kayrmac23-droid · Pull Request #6 · kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site</span><span class="truncate text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">GitHub</span></div></a></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1 mt-0.5 opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"><div class="flex items-center gap-1"><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-green-500/20 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-