he <strong>last</strong> login of the whole operation, promise. Each of these is a separate company (Resend, Vercel, VentraIP), and logins can't carry across them — but here's the thing: <strong>you don't actually have to do it in the shared browser at all.</strong> Pick whichever is less annoying:</div>
<div class="my-2"><strong>Option A — one more login, I do the fiddly bit.</strong> Log into VIPControl in the live view (same window, it's sitting on the login page), reply "in", and I'll paste all four records myself — including the 200-character DKIM string, which is the one that usually gets fumbled.</div>
<div class="my-2"><strong>Option B — you paste them, I verify.</strong> You're clearly quick in VIPControl (that <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">www</code> CNAME you added was perfect). In the zone editor for <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">replyhive.com.au</code>, add these four — same Hostname convention as your www record:</div>
<div class="overflow-x-auto"><table><thead><tr><th>Type</th><th>Hostname</th><th>Value</th><th>Priority</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>TXT</td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">resend._domainkey</code></td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">p=MIGfMA0GCSqGSIb3DQEBAQUAA4GNADCBiQKBgQC2GGz4RWs7Sw3PhUHg1y7ctoMCky5YG6bXiwouzZia8eEjUS7SAhmkz+EDMj6QIAuDM3zhXWh//a5oXTiUjlpJ7/tcL5oumgGL8pkSNdj7pUk9tvcTtd67L4drwk77Vyk0XC0XaVt/AZVx/WjC85BIImQ2HBkX35svbkynUba26wIDAQAB</code></td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>MX</td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">send</code></td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">feedback-smtp.ap-northeast-1.amazonses.com</code></td><td>10</td></tr><tr><td>TXT</td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">send</code></td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">v=spf1 include:amazonses.com ~all</code></td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>TXT</td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">_dmarc</code></td><td><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">v=DMARC1; p=none;</code></td><td>—</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<div class="my-2">Copy the DKIM value with a proper select-all — if it truncates, verification fails silently.</div>
<div class="my-2">Either way, once the records are in: reply here, I'll confirm all four resolve from my side, click <strong>Verify</strong> in Resend (I'm still logged in there from round 1), and run the final end-to-end test. Then the whole machine — site, demo, lead form, branded email — is done.</div></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1 mt-0.5 opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"><div class="flex items-center gap-1"><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-green-500/20 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-amber-500/20 hover:text-amber-600 dark:hover:text-amber-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-muted/50 hover:text-foreground" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="non