 text-sm">Reasoned</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-right size-4 text-muted-foreground/70 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg></button><div data-state="closed" id="radix-_r_43o_" hidden="" style=""></div></div><div class="-mt-2"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row" data-role="assistant" data-message-id="cmr4p9th40tpk06addzhwioyi"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 w-full items-start"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 transition-all duration-200 rounded-none py-1 pr-8 pl-0"><div><div class="prose prose-message dark:prose-invert max-w-none overflow-hidden break-words prose-code:rounded-md prose-code:bg-black/5 prose-pre:bg-black/5 prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-a:text-primary prose-pre:text-foreground prose-a:no-underline prose-pre:backdrop-blur-sm prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-a:hover:underline dark:prose-code:bg-white/10 dark:prose-pre:bg-white/10 prose-sm"><div class="my-2">Good eye — and I can see exactly why: the brand card is a <strong>composed, contained</strong> layout, while the site has no max-width container, so on a wide screen everything smears across 1920px with a huge empty right side. That's the "stretched." Two fixes, both in the card's direction:</div>
<ol>
<li><strong>Center a ~1140px content column</strong> on every section (backgrounds stay full-bleed, content stops stretching)</li>
<li><strong>Rebuild the hero as the brand card, scaled up</strong> — giant <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">replyhiv𝗲</code> wordmark, italic serif tagline, thin orange rule, mono kicker — same order, same energy</li>
</ol>
<div class="my-2">Making the edits now:</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="space-y-2 pb-4 -mt-2"><div class="min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0"><span class="group inline-flex h-7 min-w-0 max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)] items-center rounded-sm border border-border bg-muted/50 px-2 text-muted-foreground text-xs transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-pencil mr-1 h-3 w-3 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.174 6.812a1 1 0 0 0-3.986-3.987L3.842 16.174a2 2 0 0 0-.5.83l-1.321 4.352a.5.5 0 0 0 .623.622l4.353-1.32a2 2 0 0 0 .83-.497z"></path><path d="m15 5 4 4"></path></svg><span class="shrink-0 font-medium">Editing file</span><span class="mx-1.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground/50">·</span><span class="truncate text-muted-foreground/70">index.html — updating content</span></span><div class=""></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0"><span class="group inline-flex h-7 min-w-0 max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)] items-center rounded-sm border border-border bg-muted/50 px-2 text-muted-foreground text-xs transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-pencil mr-1 h-3 w-3 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.174 6.812a1 1 0 0 0-3.986-3.987L3.842 16.174a2 2 0 0 0-.5.83l-1.321 4.352a.5.5 0 0 0 .623.622l4.353-1.32a2 2 0 0 0 .83-.497z"></path><path d="m15 5 4 4"></path></svg><span class="shrink-0 font-medium">Editing file</span><span class="mx-1.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground/50">·</span><span class="truncate text-muted-foreground/70">index.html — updating content</span></span><div class=""></div></div></div><div class="min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0"><span class="group inline-flex h-7 min-w-0 max-w-[calc(100%-2re