"><div><div class="prose prose-message dark:prose-invert max-w-none overflow-hidden break-words prose-code:rounded-md prose-code:bg-black/5 prose-pre:bg-black/5 prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-a:text-primary prose-pre:text-foreground prose-a:no-underline prose-pre:backdrop-blur-sm prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-a:hover:underline dark:prose-code:bg-white/10 dark:prose-pre:bg-white/10 prose-sm"><div class="my-2">Verifying all four records from two independent resolvers, with exact-match comparison on the DKIM string (the truncation-prone one):</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="space-y-2 pb-4 -mt-2"><div class="min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0"><span class="group inline-flex h-7 min-w-0 max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)] items-center rounded-sm border border-border bg-muted/50 px-2 text-muted-foreground text-xs transition-colors cursor-pointer hover:bg-muted" role="button" aria-label="Expand details"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-terminal mr-1 h-3 w-3 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 19h8"></path><path d="m4 17 6-6-6-6"></path></svg><span class="shrink-0 font-medium">Running command</span><span class="mx-1.5 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground/50">·</span><span class="truncate text-muted-foreground/70">Verify all four Resend DNS records from two resolvers with exact DKIM comparison</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down ml-1 h-3 w-3 shrink-0 text-muted-foreground/50 transition-all group-hover:text-foreground -rotate-90" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></span><div class=""></div></div></div></div><div data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria