th><path d="m21 3-7 7"></path><path d="m3 21 7-7"></path><path d="M9 21H3v-6"></path></svg>View fullscreen</span></div></button><button type="button" class="absolute right-1.5 bottom-1.5 z-10 cursor-pointer rounded bg-black/60 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-medium text-[10px] text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors hover:bg-black/80 hover:text-white" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_r_444_" data-state="closed">v8</button></div></div></div></div></div><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row" data-role="assistant" data-message-id="cmr4pgv120v1f07adud74qwr8"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 w-full items-start"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 transition-all duration-200 rounded-none py-1 pr-8 pl-0"><div><div class="prose prose-message dark:prose-invert max-w-none overflow-hidden break-words prose-code:rounded-md prose-code:bg-black/5 prose-pre:bg-black/5 prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-a:text-primary prose-pre:text-foreground prose-a:no-underline prose-pre:backdrop-blur-sm prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-a:hover:underline dark:prose-code:bg-white/10 dark:prose-pre:bg-white/10 prose-sm"><div class="my-2">Now the last three clicks, all yours, all in your own browser:</div>
<div class="my-2"><strong>1. Verify in Resend</strong> — <a href="https://resend.com/domains" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">resend.com/domains</a> → <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">replyhive.com.au</code> → <strong>Verify DNS Records</strong>. It should flip to Verified within a minute or two; if it stays pending, wait five minutes and click again (resolver caches, nothing's wrong).</div>
<div class="my-2"><strong>2. Switch the email to your brand</strong> — once Resend shows Verified, in Vercel → Environment Variables:</div>
<ul>
<li><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_FROM_EMAIL</code> → <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">Replyhive &lt;leads@replyhive.com.au&gt;</code></li>
<li><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_TO_EMAIL</code> → <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@replyhive.com.au</code> — <strong>but first</strong> send a quick test email from your Gmail to <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@replyhive.com.au</code> and confirm it lands in your Workspace inbox. If it bounces, leave this one on your Gmail until the alias exists in Google Admin.</li>
<li>Redeploy, then submit one test lead on the live site to see the branded email arrive end-to-end.</li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2"><strong>3. Merge <a href="https://github.com/kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site/pull/6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">PR #6</a></strong> once the preview's new hero and pricing look right to you — that ships the brand-card layout and the Founding Client offer to the live domain.</div>
<div class="my-2">And the one dangling item: drag <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">og.jpg</code> from this thread into the repo root whenever you're near GitHub — then link shares unfurl with the same card your hero now mirrors.</div>
<div class="my-2">After today you've gone from <em>lead form silently dead, domain 502ing, open API proxy</em> → <strong>live domain, working funnel, hardened endpoints, founding-client pricing, and a brand-consistent site</strong>. The machine's built. Next job is pointing traffic at it.</div></div><div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"><a href="https://resend.com/domains" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group inline-flex h-16 w-44 items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border bg-card p-2 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50"><div data-slot="icon-tile" class="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-md bg-muted text-muted-foreground"><img alt="" class="size-5" src="./og_files/favicon.ico"></div><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-0.5"><span class="line-clamp-2 font-medium text-foreground text-xs leading-tight">Resend</span><span class="truncate text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">resend.com</span></div></a><a href="https://github.com/kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site/pull/6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group inline-flex h-16 w-44 items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border bg-card p-2 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50"><div data-slot="icon-tile" class="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-md bg-muted text-muted-foreground overflow-hidden"><img alt="" class="size-full object-cover" src="./og_files/6"></div><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-0.5"><span class="line-clamp-2 font-medium text-foreground text-xs leading-tight">Pricing: Founding Client offer, Standard anchor, annual option by kayrmac23-droid · Pull Request #6 · kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site</span><span class="truncate text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">GitHub</span></div></a></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1 mt-0.5 opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"><div class="flex items-center gap-1"><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg