" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-git-fork size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="3"></circle><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"></circle><path d="M18 9v2c0 .6-.4 1-1 1H7c-.6 0-1-.4-1-1V9"></path><path d="M12 12v3"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-8 mb-5"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row-reverse" data-role="user" data-message-id="cmr4pmpji0tqf07ad1zgcu9je"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 max-w-[85%] items-end"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 py-3 transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg glass-bubble-primary glass-bubble-primary--revamp text-primary-foreground" style="background: rgb(3, 21, 48); color: var(--foreground);"><div class="space-y-2"><div class="break-words text-sm"><div class="my-2 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words first:mt-0 last:mb-0">do i do the leads from email as private</div></div></div></div><span class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs">7:07 PM</span></div></div></div><div data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-_r_449_" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-1.5 text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground"><span class="font-normal text-muted-foreground/70 text-sm">Reasoned</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-right size-4 text-muted-foreground/70 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg></button><div data-state="closed" id="radix-_r_449_" hidden="" style=""></div></div><div class="-mt-2"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row" data-role="assistant" data-message-id="cmr4pnipp0yas07adf3dwkubb"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 w-full items-start"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 transition-all duration-200 rounded-none py-1 pr-8 pl-0"><div><div class="prose prose-message dark:prose-invert max-w-none overflow-hidden break-words prose-code:rounded-md prose-code:bg-black/5 prose-pre:bg-black/5 prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-a:text-primary prose-pre:text-foreground prose-a:no-underline prose-pre:backdrop-blur-sm prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-a:hover:underline dark:prose-code:bg-white/10 dark:prose-pre:bg-white/10 prose-sm"><div class="my-2">No — leave it as a normal env var. "Sensitive" (private) is for actual secrets, and <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_FROM_EMAIL</code> is just an email address: it's stamped on every email you send anyway, so there's nothing to protect. Marking it sensitive only makes it annoying later (you can't view the value in the dashboard again, just replace it). Same logic for <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_TO_EMAIL</code>.</div>
<div class="my-2">The ones that <em>deserve</em> the Sensitive toggle are <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">RESEND_API_KEY</code> and <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</code> — real credentials. (If you already saved those as plain, no panic: Vercel encrypts all env vars at rest either way; Sensitive just also hides them from dashboard eyes. Flip them if it's easy, don't lose sleep if not.)</div>
<div class="my-2">While you're in there, the exact value to paste:</div>
<ul>
<li><code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_FROM_EMAIL</code> → <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">Replyhive &lt;leads@replyhive.com.au&gt;</code> — keep the display name and angle brackets exactly like that</li>
<li>Then <strong>redeploy</strong> (env changes only apply to new deployments), and fire one test lead from the live site to see the branded email arrive.</li>
</ul></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1 mt-0.5 opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"><div class="flex items-center gap-1"><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-green-500/20 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-amber-500/20 hover:text-amber-600 dark:hover:text-amber-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-muted/50 hover:text-foreground" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 text-muted-foreground/50 transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50 hover:text-foreground" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-git-fork size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="3"></circle><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"></circle><path d="M18 9v2c0 .6-.4 1-1 1H7c-.6 0-1-.4-1-1V9"></path><path d="M12 12v3"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-8 mb-5"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row-reverse" data-role="user" data-message-id="cmr4ptg5p0uma07adid1sh83b"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 max-w-[85%] items-end"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 py-3 transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg glass-bubble-primary glass-bubble-primary--revamp text-primary-foreground" style="background: rgb(3, 21, 48); color: var(--foreground);"><div class="space-y-2"><div class="break-words text-sm"><div class="my-2 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words first:mt-0 last:mb-0">i think im kay@replyhive</div></div></div></div><span class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs">7:12 PM</span></div></div></div><div data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-_r_460_" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-1.5 text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground"><span class="font-normal text-muted-foreground/70 text-sm">Reasoned</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-right size-4 text-muted-foreground/70 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg></button><div data-state="closed" id="radix-_r_460_" hidden="" style=""></div></div><div class="-mt-2"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row" data-role="assistant" data-message-id="cmr4pui2c0u5k07ad9jwx71dx"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 w-full items-start"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 transition-all duration-200 rounded-none py-1 pr-8 pl-0"><div><div class="prose prose-message dark:prose-invert max-w-none overflow-hidden break-words prose-code:rounded-md prose-code:bg-black/5 prose-pre:bg-black/5 prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-a:text-primary prose-pre:text-foreground prose-a:no-underline prose-pre:backdrop-blur-sm prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-a:hover:underline dark:prose-code:bg-white/10 dark:prose-pre:bg-white/10 prose-sm"><div class="my-2">That's an easy one to square away — and worth doing properly, because the site tells people to email <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@replyhive.com.au</code> in four places (the CTA, the footer, and the form's error fallbacks). If <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@</code> doesn't exist, those are all dead ends for a prospect whose form submission just failed.</div>
<div class="my-2">The 2-minute fix: <strong>make <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@</code> an alias of your real mailbox.</strong> Free, no new user licence:</div>
<ol>
<li>First confirm your actual address: send yourself a test from Gmail to <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">kay@replyhive.com.au</code> — if it lands, that's your mailbox.</li>
<li><strong>admin.google.com</strong> → Directory → <strong>Users</strong> → click yourself → <strong>User information</strong> → <strong>Email aliases</strong> → add <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello</code> → Save. (Takes effect within a few minutes.)</li>
<li>Test again from Gmail to <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@replyhive.com.au</code> — it should drop into the same inbox as kay@.</li>
<li>Then set <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_TO_EMAIL</code> → <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">hello@replyhive.com.au</code> in Vercel and redeploy — leads, the site's mailto links, and your public contact address all line up on one inbox.</li>
</ol>
<div class="my-2">If you'd rather skip the alias today: set <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_TO_EMAIL</code> → <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">kay@replyhive.com.au</code> and leads will flow fine — just know the "email us directly" fallback on the site stays broken until the alias exists, so do it soon.</div>
<div class="my-2">One thing that does <strong>not</strong> need a mailbox: <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">LEAD_FROM_EMAIL</code> (<code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">Replyhive &lt;leads@replyhive.com.au&gt;</code>). That's only a sending identity through Resend — when you hit reply on a lead email, it goes to the <em>prospect</em> (reply-to is wired to their address), so <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">leads@</code> never needs an inbox.</div></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1 mt-0.5 opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100"><div class="flex items-center gap-1"><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-green-500/20 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-amber-500/20 hover:text-amber-600 dark:hover:text-amber-400" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-down size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"></path><path d="M17 14V2"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 transition-colors text-muted-foreground/50 hover:bg-muted/50 hover:text-foreground" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></button><button class="rounded p-1 text-muted-foreground/50 transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50 hover:text-foreground" data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-git-fork size-3.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="3"></circle><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"></circle><path d="M18 9v2c0 .6-.4 1-1 1H7c-.6 0-1-.4-1-1V9"></path><path d="M12 12v3"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-8 mb-5"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row-reverse" data-role="user" data-message-id="cmr4q6x6h0tyj07admtqie4r1"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 max-w-[85%] items-end"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 py-3 transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg glass-bubble-primary glass-bubble-primary--revamp text-primary-foreground" style="background: rgb(3, 21, 48); color: var(--foreground);"><div class="space-y-2"><div class="break-words text-sm"><div class="my-2 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words first:mt-0 last:mb-0">wheres #6 and where do i drag it to</div></div></div></div><span class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground/70 text-xs">7:23 PM</span></div></div></div><div data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-_r_46n_" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-1.5 text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground"><span class="font-normal text-muted-foreground/70 text-sm">Reasoned</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-right size-4 text-muted-foreground/70 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg></button><div data-state="closed" id="radix-_r_46n_" hidden="" style=""></div></div><div class="-mt-2"><div class="group relative flex min-w-0 gap-3 flex-row" data-role="assistant" data-message-id="cmr4q7wgk0un107ad6m2x04b8"><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-1 w-full items-start"><div class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden break-words px-4 transition-all duration-200 rounded-none py-1 pr-8 pl-0"><div><div class="prose prose-message dark:prose-invert max-w-none overflow-hidden break-words prose-code:rounded-md prose-code:bg-black/5 prose-pre:bg-black/5 prose-code:px-1.5 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-a:text-primary prose-pre:text-foreground prose-a:no-underline prose-pre:backdrop-blur-sm prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none prose-a:hover:underline dark:prose-code:bg-white/10 dark:prose-pre:bg-white/10 prose-sm"><div class="my-2">Both links, both answers:</div>
<h2>PR #6 — the pricing + layout changes</h2>
