</ol>
<div class="my-2">That's it — it deploys itself. Order doesn't matter (the upload and PR #6 don't touch the same files), so do either first. Once both are in, tell me and I'll confirm <code class="rounded-md bg-black/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm dark:bg-white/10">replyhive.com.au/og.jpg</code> loads and run the full final sweep — live layout, demo, lead pipeline, share tags, everything.</div></div><div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"><a href="https://github.com/kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site/pull/6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group inline-flex h-16 w-44 items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border bg-card p-2 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50"><div data-slot="icon-tile" class="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-md bg-muted text-muted-foreground overflow-hidden"><img alt="" class="size-full object-cover" src="./og_files/6"></div><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-0.5"><span class="line-clamp-2 font-medium text-foreground text-xs leading-tight">Pricing: Founding Client offer, Standard anchor, annual option by kayrmac23-droid · Pull Request #6 · kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site</span><span class="truncate text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">GitHub</span></div></a><a href="https://github.com/kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group inline-flex h-16 w-44 items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border bg-card p-2 no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50"><div data-slot="icon-tile" class="flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-md bg-muted text-muted-foreground overflow-hidden"><img alt="" class="size-full object-cover" src="./og_files/Fieldr-site"></div><div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-0.5"><span class="line-clamp-2 font-medium text-foreground text-xs leading-tight">GitHub - kayrmac23-droid/Fieldr-site: AI assistant landing page for Fieldr</span><span class="truncate text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">GitHub</span></div></a></div></div><div class="flex 